snippet.title: DIY Perks
snippet.description:
I'm Matt, and here on DIY Perks you'll find plenty of interesting DIY projects on a variety of topics, including computers, woodworking, electronics, audio, and more!
I hope you enjoy my content, and please consider subscribing if you do!

EMAIL...

For project questions, the best way is either on Patreon or the Patreon chat server: http://patreon.com/diyperks as I get too many emails to keep up with.

However if you want to get in touch with me directly for sponsorship enquiries, fan mail, or just to say 'hi' (no project questions please) then send an email to diyperks@gmail.com - I do get quite a few though so please allow 7 days for a response.
